<p>But the SKIMS mogul is still keeping her fans updated with the most private aspects of her life, thanks to the wonders of social media.</p>

<p>She prepared to tackle her acne Monday, as she took to her Instagram Story during a visit from celebrity dermatologist and YouTube sensation Sandra Lee (AKA Dr. Pimple Popper).</p>

