<p>The KKW Beauty founder shares daughters North, Chicago, two, sons Saint, four, and Psalm, one, with husband Kanye West, 43, whom she married in 2014. </p>

<p>She reportedly ushered in the end of KUWTK, as she and little sister Kylie Jenner, 23, both threatened to leave, forcing 'momager' Kris Jenner's hand. </p>

<p>A source told The Sun that Kanye was her reason for quitting: 'The family have been locked in an ongoing debate over the future of the show for months now.</p>

<p>'Kim has all the drama with Kanye West going on. He's refusing to put anything personal on the show, and it's increasingly difficult for Kim to find time to film the show.'</p>

<p>Kim and the Yeezy mogul have been facing marital issues amid quarantine and his bizarre last-minute presidential bid, which has given the family cause for concern over his mental health.         </p>

